         <ab>VrS89.24 (mss. 2005, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2102, 2104, 2106, 4000, 4010, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4161, 4162, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            rāspīg pad gāh ī frabardārān <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō yō zaōtā frā.mē mrūte</em> zōt <em>aθā ratuš</em> kardan</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "The <em>rāspīg</em> (should recite) at the place of the <em>frabardārān: yaθā ahū vairiiō yō zaōtā frā.mē mrūte</em>. The <em>zōt</em> should answer: <em>aθā ratuš</em>."</ab>
